根据具有管辖权的海牙的一个国际委员会的调查，厄立特里亚违反国际法入侵埃塞俄比亚引发这场战争。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/4548754.stm |title=International commission: Eritrea triggered the border war with Ethiopia |publisher=BBC News |date=2005-12-21 |accessdate=November 2012 |archive-date=2012-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320123623/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/4548754.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

战争结束时，埃塞俄比亚占据了所有争议土地并攻入厄立特里亚腹地。<ref>Andrew England ([[美联社|美联社]]). [http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/500000-flee-as-ethiopian-troops-storm-eritrea-718957.html 500,000 flee as Ethiopian troops storm Eritrea] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/500000-flee-as-ethiopian-troops-storm-eritrea-718957.html |date=20200409000117 }}, [[独立报|独立报]],  18 May 2000.</ref>联合国安理会批准组建的埃塞俄比亚-厄立特里亚边界委员会裁决战争冲突的北部核心地区的主要城镇[[巴德梅|巴德梅]]归属厄立特里亚。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dehai.org/demarcation-watch/eebc/EEBC-President-Report-to-UN-16.pdf |title=Annex I. Eritrea-Ethiopia Boundary Commission. Sixteenth report on the work of the Commission. (S/2005/142) |year=2005 |page=5 § 20 |accessdate=November 2012 |archive-date=2016-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318202129/http://dehai.org/demarcation-watch/eebc/EEBC-President-Report-to-UN-16.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 但{{As of|2014}}埃塞俄比亚仍然占据这一地区。南线争议的核心区是{{tsl|en|Bure}}归属埃塞俄比亚。中线争议的{{tsl|en|Tsorona-Zalambessa}}区域被裁决分别归属于两国。

==背景==
从1961年至1991年，衣索比亞歷經了[[厄利垂亞獨立戰爭|厄利垂亞獨立戰爭]]和[[衣索比亞內戰|衣索比亞內戰]]。内戰于1974年9月12日爆發，[[门格斯图|门格斯图]]发动军事政变推翻[[衣索比亞皇帝|衣索比亞皇帝]][[海尔·塞拉西一世|海尔·塞拉西一世]]。<ref name="dates"/>内战持续到1991年，[[提格雷人民解放阵线|提格雷人民解放阵线]]（提人陣）领导的[[衣索比亞人民革命民主陣線|衣索比亞人民革命民主陣線]]（衣革陣）推翻了政权建立起过渡政府。<ref name="dates">{{cite web|first=A. Valentino |last=Benjamin |title=Final Solutions: Mass Killing and Genocide in the Twentieth Century |year=2004 |page=196}}</ref>

在内战中，提格雷人民解放阵线与[[厄利垂亞人民解放陣線|厄利垂亞人民解放陣線]]（厄人阵）為盟友。1991年，在联合国安排下，厄利垂亞人民解放阵线成立过渡自治政府並於2年后經公投独立并加入联合国。{{sfn|Abbink|2003|p=221}}<ref name=Briggs-28-29>{{cite book |last=Briggs |first=Philip |last2=Blatt |first2=Brian|year=2009 |title=Ethiopia |edition=5, illustrated |series=Bradt Guides |publisher=Bradt Travel Guides |isbn=1-84162-284-2 |pages=[http://books.google.com/books?id=QFb6pacaczsC&lpg=PP28&pg=PA28#v=onepage&q&f=false 28,29]}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1070861.stm |title=Timeline: Eritrea |publisher=BBC |date=7 May 2011 |accessdate=August 2011 |archive-date=2011-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811201019/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1070861.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1991年，双方成立一个委员会解决过渡期的任何争议问题。<ref name="Alemseged">{{cite web | last = Tesfai | first = Alemseged | title = The Cause of the Eritrean–Ethiopian Border Conflict | url = http://www.dehai.org/conflict/analysis/alemsghed1.html | accessdate = 2006-08-02 | archive-date = 2018-01-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180113064621/http://www.dehai.org/conflict/analysis/alemsghed1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>但双方关系仍日益恶化。<ref name=Briggs-28-29/>

内战期间，双方同意按照当时的行政区界划界。但厄利垂亞独立后，双方都不同意照此划界，分别追溯到1935年前義大利與衣索比亞的划界协定与条约。<ref>{{cite book |last=Mussie |first=Tesfagiorgis G. |year=2010 |chapter=Eritrean colonial boundaries |title=Eritrea |series=Africa in Focus |edition=illustrated |publisher=ABC-CLIO |isbn=1-59884-231-5 |pages=[http://books.google.com/books?id=f0R7iHoaykoC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA53#v=onepage&q&f=false 53–54]}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Shapland |first=Greg |year= 1997 |title=Rivers of discord: international water disputes in the Middle East |publisher=C. Hurst & Co|isbn=1-85065-214-7 |page= [http://books.google.com/books?id=VDKJV-916UoC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA71#v=onepage&q&f=false 71]}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Degefu |first=Gebre Tsadik |year=2003 |title=The Nile: Historical, Legal and Developmental Perspectives |edition=illustrated |publisher=Trafford Publishing |isbn=1-4120-0056-4 |pages=[http://books.google.com/books?id=aK9Vjj5i4NUC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA94#v=onepage&q&f=false 94–99]}}</ref>1997年11月28日，厄利垂亞发行新货币[[纳克法|纳克法]]，衣索比亞因此对厄利垂亞实施经济抵制，雙方关系急剧恶化。

厄利垂亞总统[[伊薩亞斯·阿費沃爾基|伊薩亞斯·阿費沃爾基]]战前认为可以吞并[[巴德梅|巴德梅]]，{{sfn|Abbink|2003|p=221,226}}<ref>“[[梅莱斯|梅莱斯]]是脆弱的可以被战争推翻”。 ({{cite news |first=Richard |last=Dowden |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/commentators/there-are-no-winners-in-this-insane-and-destructive-war-714305.html |title=There are no winners in this insane and destructive war |newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |date=2 June 2000 |location=London |accessdate=2014-11-10 |archive-date=2008-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212163222/http://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/commentators/there-are-no-winners-in-this-insane-and-destructive-war-714305.html |dead-url=no }})</ref>但是巴德梅位于衣索比亞执政党的发源地提格雷省，是许多衣索比亞政要的故乡（包括[[梅莱斯·泽纳维|梅莱斯·泽纳维]]），衣索比亞政府出于政治压力不会妥协。{{sfn|Abbink|2003|p=221,226}}

==战争==

===经过===
在巴德梅附近的边界冲突，<ref name=Connell>{{cite web |last=Connell |first=Dan |editor-last=Woods |editor-first=Emira |date=2 October 2005 |url=http://www.fpif.org/articles/eritreaethiopia_war_looms |title=Eritrea/Ethiopia War Looms |publisher=Foreign Policy in Focus (FPIF) |accessdate=2014-11-10 |archive-date=2020-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200409000108/https://fpif.org/eritreaethiopia_war_looms/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1998年5月6日一支厄利垂亞的机械化部队进入巴德梅地区。<ref name=Connell/><ref>Richard Dowden ''[http://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/commentators/there-are-no-winners-in-this-insane-and-destructive-war-714305.html There are no winners in this insane and destructive war] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/commentators/there-are-no-winners-in-this-insane-and-destructive-war-714305.html |date=20081212163222 }}'', [[The_Independent|The Independent]],  2 June 2000</ref>

{{quotation|14. 有证据表明，1998年5月12日凌晨5时30分，至少两个旅的[[厄利垂亞陸軍|厄利垂亞陸軍]]在坦克和大炮支援下进攻巴德梅和衣索比亞的{{tsl|en|Tahtay Adiyabo|Tahtay Adiabo Wereda}}多處邊界以及在附近的{{tsl|en|La'ilay Adiyabo|Laelay Adiabo Wereda}}两处地区。当天及次日，厄利垂亞陸軍通过巴德梅平原占据衣索比亞东部高地。虽然衣索比亞國防軍卷入此冲突，但有证据表明衣索比亞方的主要防御者是当地的民兵与警察，并很快被迫撤走。由于不存在对厄利垂亞的军事进攻，5月12日的战斗不能被判断是符合联合国宪章的自卫。<br><br>
